==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Numeric
<hw>Nu*mer"ic</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Math.)</fld> <def>Any number,
proper or improper fraction, or incommensurable ratio. The term also
includes any imaginary expression like <mathex>m + n⟦root⟧-1</mathex>,
where <it>m</it> and <it>n</it> are real <xex>numerics</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

